snippet.title: Paper Plane Arena - The Haunted House // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2722870/Paper_Plane_Arena__The_Haunted_House/

Paper Plane Arena is an interactive game experience that is designed to ease your mind and have fun popping innocent balloons. You jump into the role of a little paper plane that is supposed to rescue the world from little but evil balloon demons by dashing through them.

Developed by
@epixrgames828
